Invocation Name: vintage video
des:
Watch vintage educational videos on dating, social etiquette, family, friendship, health, economics, morality, military and civics from the late 40s and 50s. Requires Echo Show.

All films, images and sounds available under a Creative Commons Public Domain License from the Prelinger collection at The Internet Archive.

All icons from the Noun Project. (movie reel by Josue Oquendo + finger scroll by Juraj Sedlák).
